","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1166,"output":216,"cacheRead":21120,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22502,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775229280999}}
{"type":"message","id":"d3af4211","parentId":"10f9bc36","timestamp":"2026-04-03T15:14:47.024Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_3eJPlhuo6VhXGoZVme7miv2h|fc_0369f6bbd751daf50169cfd966678081938bda82096c3af6b9","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\n\n- **Name:**\n- **What to call them:**\n- **Pronouns:** _(optional)_\n- **Timezone:**\n- **Notes:**\n\n## Context\n\n_(What do they care about? What projects are they working on? What annoys them? What makes them laugh? Build this over time.)_\n\n---\n\nThe more you know, the better you can help. But remember — you're learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775229287022}}
