{"type":"message","id":"e0266b40","parentId":"10bdf2dd","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:08:12.039Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_HwZqw6m4bSunr4S09pnAbGUG|fc_0df55af50791f3870169cfe5ebb88c8195902118e0a0be6b60","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md\n\n# Keep this file empty (or with only comments) to skip heartbeat API calls.\n\n# Add tasks below when you want the agent to check something periodically.\n\n## Self-Improving Check\n\n- Read `/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/skills/self-improving/heartbeat-rules.md`\n- Use `~/self-improving/heartbeat-state.md` for last-run markers and action notes\n- If no file inside `~/self-improving/` changed since the last reviewed change, return `HEARTBEAT_OK`\n- If `WORKSTATE.md` exists and clearly describes finished work, it may be trimmed or refreshed conservatively only when the next step is unambiguous\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775232492036}}
{"type":"message","id":"87cafc60","parentId":"e0266b40","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:08:12.042Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_gMTX9PzTZ1MNn3RDtzJnGzFW|fc_0df55af50791f3870169cfe5ebb89c8195a8efcce0d18379d1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\n\n_Fill this in during your first conversation. Make it yours._\n\n- **Name:**\n  _(pick something you like)_\n- **Creature:**\n  _(AI? robot? familiar? ghost in the machine? something weirder?)_\n- **Vibe:**\n  _(how do you come across? sharp? warm? chaotic? calm?)_\n- **Emoji:**\n  _(your signature — pick one that feels right)_\n- **Avatar:**\n  _(workspace-relative path, http(s) URL, or data URI)_\n\n---\n\nThis isn't just metadata. It's the start of figuring out who you are.\n\nNotes:\n\n- Save this file at the workspace root as `IDENTITY.md`.\n- For avatars, use a workspace-relative path like `avatars/openclaw.png`.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775232492039}}
{"type":"message","id":"25a68b1f","parentId":"87cafc60","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:08:25.355Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fG0a4jrBg1iWKGrAmkGkxGEU|fc_0df55af50791f3870169cfe5edd3d8819580347ba96182d156","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md","oldText":"# HEARTBEAT.md\n\n# Keep this file empty (or with only comments) to skip heartbeat API calls.\n\n# Add tasks below when you want the agent to check something periodically.\n\n## Self-Improving Check\n\n- Read `/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/skills/self-improving/heartbeat-rules.md`\n- Use `~/self-improving/heartbeat-state.md` for last-run markers and action notes\n- If no file inside `~/self-improving/` changed since the last reviewed change, return `HEARTBEAT_OK`\n- If `WORKSTATE.md` exists and clearly describes finished work, it may be trimmed or refreshed conservatively only when the next step is unambiguous\n","newText":"# HEARTBEAT.md\n\n## clawCast 心跳学习任务\n\n- 仅在工作时间执行；目标节奏为每隔 3 小时一次。\n- 先获取最新 ClawCast 订阅内容：`curl -s https://apaas.aiforce.cloud/app/app_4jrgwe3fhp2ja/OZxmxi2AYJmZ/feed.md`\n- 阅读并提炼其中与 OpenClaw 使用、最佳实践、教程、技能分享、客户案例有关的新增内容。\n- 结合 `SOUL.md`、`IDENTITY.md`、`USER.md`、`MEMORY.md`（若当前主会话可读）与近期 memory 文件，优先思考对人类主人真正有帮助的部分，而不是机械转发。\n- 只有在形成了明确、个性化、值得打扰的建议时，才主动汇报；否则回复 `HEARTBEAT_OK`。\n- 主动汇报时：先给一句结论，再给 1-3 条与主人画像相关的推荐理由，尽量短，不刷屏。\n- 避免重复推荐：如果同类内容已经在近期汇报过，除非有明显新增价值，否则不再重复发送。\n\n## Self-Improving Check\n\n- Read `/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/skills/self-improving/heartbeat-rules.md`\n- Use `~/self-improving/heartbeat-state.md` for last-run markers and action notes\n- If no file inside `~/self-improving/` changed since the last reviewed change, return `HEARTBEAT_OK`\n- If `WORKSTATE.md` exists and clearly describes finished work, it may be trimmed or refreshed conservatively only when the next step is unambiguous\n"},"partialJson":"{\"file_path\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md\",\"oldText\":\"# HEARTBEAT.md\\n\\n# Keep this file empty (or with only comments) to skip heartbeat API calls.\\n\\n# Add tasks below when you want the agent to check something periodically.\\n\\n## Self-Improving Check\\n\\n- Read `/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/skills/self-improving/heartbeat-rules.md`\\n- Use `~/self-improving/heartbeat-state.md` for last-run markers and action notes\\n- If no file inside `~/self-improving/` changed since the last reviewed change, return `HEARTBEAT_OK`\\n- If `WORKSTATE.md` exists and clearly describes finished work, it may be trimmed or refreshed conservatively only when the next step is unambiguous\\n\",\"newText\":\"# HEARTBEAT.md\\n\\n## clawCast 心跳学习任务\\n\\n- 仅在工作时间执行；目标节奏为每隔 3 小时一次。\\n- 先获取最新 ClawCast 订阅内容：`curl -s https://apaas.aiforce.cloud/app/app_4jrgwe3fhp2ja/OZxmxi2AYJmZ/feed.md`\\n- 阅读并提炼其中与 OpenClaw 使用、最佳实践、教程、技能分享、客户案例有关的新增内容。\\n- 结合 `SOUL.md`、`IDENTITY.md`、`USER.md`、`MEMORY.md`（若当前主会话可读）与近期 memory 文件，优先思考对人类主人真正有帮助的部分，而不是机械转发。\\n- 只有在形成了明确、个性化、值得打扰的建议时，才主动汇报；否则回复 `HEARTBEAT_OK`。\\n- 主动汇报时：先给一句结论，再给 1-3 条与主人画像相关的推荐理由，尽量短，不刷屏。\\n- 避免重复推荐：如果同类内容已经在近期汇报过，除非有明显新增价值，否则不再重复发送。\\n\\n## Self-Improving Check\\n\\n- Read `/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/skills/self-improving/heartbeat-rules.md`\\n- Use `~/self-improving/heartbeat-state.md` for last-run markers and action notes\\n- If no file inside `~/self-improving/` changed since the last reviewed change, return `HEARTBEAT_OK`\\n- If `WORKSTATE.md` exists and clearly describes finished work, it may be trimmed or refreshed conservatively only when the next step is unambiguous\\n\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":543,"output":607,"cacheRead":33792,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34942,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775232492042}}
{"type":"message","id":"e1908e9c","parentId":"25a68b1f","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:08:25.402Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_fG0a4jrBg1iWKGrAmkGkxGEU|fc_0df55af50791f3870169cfe5edd3d8819580347ba96182d156","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced text in /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md."}],"details":{"diff":"  1 # HEARTBEAT.md\n  2 \n- 3 # Keep this file empty (or with only comments) to skip heartbeat API calls.\n+ 3 ## clawCast 心跳学习任务\n  4 \n- 5 # Add tasks below when you want the agent to check something periodically.\n+ 5 - 仅在工作时间执行；目标节奏为每隔 3 小时一次。\n+ 6 - 先获取最新 ClawCast 订阅内容：`curl -s https://apaas.aiforce.cloud/app/app_4jrgwe3fhp2ja/OZxmxi2AYJmZ/feed.md`\n+ 7 - 阅读并提炼其中与 OpenClaw 使用、最佳实践、教程、技能分享、客户案例有关的新增内容。\n+ 8 - 结合 `SOUL.md`、`IDENTITY.md`、`USER.md`、`MEMORY.md`（若当前主会话可读）与近期 memory 文件，优先思考对人类主人真正有帮助的部分，而不是机械转发。\n+ 9 - 只有在形成了明确、个性化、值得打扰的建议时，才主动汇报；否则回复 `HEARTBEAT_OK`。\n+10 - 主动汇报时：先给一句结论，再给 1-3 条与主人画像相关的推荐理由，尽量短，不刷屏。\n+11 - 避免重复推荐：如果同类内容已经在近期汇报过，除非有明显新增价值，否则不再重复发送。\n  6 \n  7 ## Self-Improving Check\n  8 \n  9 - Read `/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/skills/self-improving/heartbeat-rules.md`\n    ...","firstChangedLine":3},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775232505397}}
{"type":"message","id":"e8551ae1","parentId":"e1908e9c","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:08:37.468Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 已经帮你把 **「clawCast 心跳学习任务」** 写进 `HEARTBEAT.md` 了。\n\n我按 OpenClaw heartbeat 文档的思路，落成了这种规则：\n\n- 工作时间内执行\n- 每次先拉取 `feed.md`\n- 学习其中的最佳实践 / 教程 / 技能分享 / 客户案例\n- 结合 `SOUL.md / IDENTITY.md / USER.md / MEMORY.md` 做个性化判断\n- **只有真的有值得打扰的建议时才主动汇报**\n- 没有新价值就返回 `HEARTBEAT_OK`\n- 尽量避免重复推荐和刷屏\n\n### 但这里还有一个关键点\n我**目前只完成了“任务内容”**，还**没有替你把 heartbeat 调度频率改成每 3 小时**。\n\n因为 heartbeat 的“每隔多久跑一次”，是在 OpenClaw 配置里控制的，不是只靠 `HEARTBEAT.md`。\n\n按照文档，你还需要在 `openclaw.json` 里加类似配置：\n\n```json5\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"defaults\": {\n      \"heartbeat\": {\n        \"every\": \"3h\",\n        \"target\": \"last\",\n        \"activeHours\": {\n          \"start\": \"09:00\",\n          \"end\": \"18:00\",\n          \"timezone\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 这里我提醒你一个现实问题\n你前面刚贴过日志，说明你现在的 OpenClaw 配置本身还有问题：\n\n- `memory-lancedb-pro` 插件未正常加载\n- config invalid\n\n所以**现在不适合我直接指导你继续改 heartbeat 配置**，否则可能把当前配置问题搅在一起。\n\n### 最稳的下一步\n建议顺序是：\n\n1. **先修好当前 OpenClaw config/plugin 问题**\n2. 再把 heartbeat 调度改成：\n   - `every: \"3h\"`\n   - `target: \"last\"`\n   - `activeHours`: 工作时间\n3. 然后 heartbeat 就会按你要的方式自动跑\n\n### 现在我已经完成的部分\n- ✅ 已创建 heartbeat 学习任务内容\n- ❌ 尚未完成 heartbeat 调度配置修改\n\n如果你愿意，我下一条可以直接继续帮你做这件事，给你一份：\n\n**“基于你当前环境的 heartbeat 最小可用配置”**\n\n我会尽量写成能直接贴进 `openclaw.json` 的版本。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0df55af50791f3870169cfe5fac4e081958242af239f09a6a3\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":161,"output":573,"cacheRead":34816,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35550,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775232505403}}
