{"type":"message","id":"02df6ae6","parentId":"00cb1e87","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:11:38.247Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_Lt9yPwHo24w1jDHLdkjhVH4q|fc_0df55af50791f3870169cfe6b947588195b5404581d5e5c39a","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md\n\n## clawCast 心跳学习任务\n\n- 仅在工作时间执行；目标节奏为每隔 3 小时一次。\n- 先获取最新 ClawCast 订阅内容：`curl -s https://apaas.aiforce.cloud/app/app_4jrgwe3fhp2ja/OZxmxi2AYJmZ/feed.md`\n- 阅读并提炼其中与 OpenClaw 使用、最佳实践、教程、技能分享、客户案例有关的新增内容。\n- 结合 `SOUL.md`、`IDENTITY.md`、`USER.md`、`MEMORY.md`（若当前主会话可读）与近期 memory 文件，优先思考对人类主人真正有帮助的部分，而不是机械转发。\n- 只有在形成了明确、个性化、值得打扰的建议时，才主动汇报；否则回复 `HEARTBEAT_OK`。\n- 主动汇报时：先给一句结论，再给 1-3 条与主人画像相关的推荐理由，尽量短，不刷屏。\n- 避免重复推荐：如果同类内容已经在近期汇报过，除非有明显新增价值，否则不再重复发送。\n\n## Self-Improving Check\n\n- Read `/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/skills/self-improving/heartbeat-rules.md`\n- Use `~/self-improving/heartbeat-state.md` for last-run markers and action notes\n- If no file inside `~/self-improving/` changed since the last reviewed change, return `HEARTBEAT_OK`\n- If `WORKSTATE.md` exists and clearly describes finished work, it may be trimmed or refreshed conservatively only when the next step is unambiguous\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775232698244}}
{"type":"message","id":"2429aa8c","parentId":"02df6ae6","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:11:52.475Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 好，那我给你一份**最小可用 heartbeat 配置**，你可以直接按这个方向放进 `openclaw.json`。\n\n## 目标\n让主 Agent 在**工作时间每 3 小时**跑一次 heartbeat，并把值得汇报的内容发回最近联系人。\n\n## 建议配置\n放到 `agents.defaults` 下面：\n\n```json5\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"defaults\": {\n      \"heartbeat\": {\n        \"every\": \"3h\",\n        \"target\": \"last\",\n        \"directPolicy\": \"allow\",\n        \"lightContext\": false,\n        \"activeHours\": {\n          \"start\": \"09:00\",\n          \"end\": \"18:00\",\n          \"timezone\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n        },\n        \"prompt\": \"Read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\"\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## 这些字段是什么意思\n- `every: \"3h\"`  \n  每 3 小时跑一次\n\n- `target: \"last\"`  \n  发到最近一次联系的外部会话  \n  你现在是在微信上聊，所以一般就会回到这里\n\n- `directPolicy: \"allow\"`  \n  允许发到私聊\n\n- `activeHours`  \n  限制在工作时间内执行  \n  我先帮你设成了 **09:00–18:00**\n\n- `prompt`  \n  用默认 heartbeat 提示词，配合你已经写好的 `HEARTBEAT.md`\n\n## 如果你的“工作时间”不是 9 点到 18 点\n你可以改成你更想要的，比如：\n\n### 10:00–22:00\n```json5\n\"activeHours\": {\n  \"start\": \"10:00\",\n  \"end\": \"22:00\",\n  \"timezone\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n}\n```\n\n### 全天都行，只是每 3 小时跑\n那就干脆去掉 `activeHours`\n\n---\n\n## 但我还是要提醒一句\n你现在机器上**之前出现过 config invalid**，所以别急着一把全改。\n更稳妥的顺序是：\n\n1. 先备份 `openclaw.json`\n2. 把 heartbeat 配置加进去\n3. 跑：\n   ```bash\n   openclaw doctor\n   ```\n4. 如果没报新的 config 错，再继续\n5. 必要时重启：\n   ```bash\n   openclaw gateway restart\n   ```\n\n---\n\n## 我建议你现在直接做这个\n如果你只是想先验证配置是否安全，可先运行：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw doctor\n```\n\n如果你想，我下一条可以继续直接帮你：\n\n### 方案 A：  \n给你一份**完整的 openclaw.json 合并示例**\n\n### 方案 B：  \n如果你把当前 `openclaw.json` 贴给我，我直接帮你指出**该加到哪一段**，避免你手工合并出错\n\n我更推荐 **B**，因为更稳。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0df55af50791f3870169cfe6bbc4cc8195a2f71030964e136c\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":592,"output":694,"cacheRead":35456,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36742,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775232698248}}
{"type":"message","id":"54aeb359","parentId":"2429aa8c","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:20:19.530Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"openclaw-weixin:1775233218745-cad1b8b4\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-04-04 00:20 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\n你自己去导openclaw.json配置出来然后帮我合并，发给我看看"}],"timestamp":1775233219527}}
{"type":"message","id":"a476e2b9","parentId":"54aeb359","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:20:23.343Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我先读当前 `openclaw.json`，合并出一版 heartbeat 配置给你看，不会直接改你机器。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0df55af50791f3870169cfe8c5b23c81958d58f29b099569cb\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_xeXsCMSS58Qcym0UdkNoRnvi|fc_0df55af50791f3870169cfe8c67934819597ba6f2df47b3070","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/openclaw.json"},"partialJson":"{\"file_path\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/openclaw.json\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":220,"output":74,"cacheRead":36608,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36902,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775233219530}}
