{"type":"message","id":"bacc37d3","parentId":"5abe698a","timestamp":"2026-04-03T16:21:04.023Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 我已经把你当前的 `openclaw.json` 读出来了，并且先做了**合并预览**。\n\n先说重点：  \n**你的文件里有明文密钥和 token。** 我不会在这里原样回贴完整配置，避免把敏感信息再扩散一遍。  \n我给你的是**已脱敏、带 heartbeat 合并后的预览版**，你可以看结构对不对。\n\n---\n\n## 这是合并后的关键结果\n\n你当前配置里，应该把 heartbeat 加到这里：\n\n```json5\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"defaults\": {\n      \"models\": {\n        \"openai/gpt-5.4\": {}\n      },\n      \"workspace\": \"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace\",\n      \"compaction\": {\n        \"mode\": \"safeguard\"\n      },\n      \"elevatedDefault\": \"full\",\n      \"heartbeat\": {\n        \"every\": \"3h\",\n        \"target\": \"last\",\n        \"directPolicy\": \"allow\",\n        \"lightContext\": false,\n        \"activeHours\": {\n          \"start\": \"09:00\",\n          \"end\": \"18:00\",\n          \"timezone\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n        },\n        \"prompt\": \"Read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\"\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 按你当前文件结构，合并后的脱敏预览长这样\n\n```json5\n{\n  \"meta\": {\n    \"lastTouchedVersion\": \"2026.3.13\",\n    \"lastTouchedAt\": \"2026-03-28T07:43:37.279Z\"\n  },\n  \"models\": {\n    \"providers\": {\n      \"openai\": {\n        \"baseUrl\": \"http://***:8080/v1\",\n        \"apiKey\": \"***\",\n        \"models\": [\n          {\n            \"id\": \"gpt-5.4\",\n            \"name\": \"GPT-5.4\"\n          }\n        ]\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"defaults\": {\n      \"models\": {\n        \"openai/gpt-5.4\": {}\n      },\n      \"workspace\": \"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace\",\n      \"compaction\": {\n        \"mode\": \"safeguard\"\n      },\n      \"elevatedDefault\": \"full\",\n      \"heartbeat\": {\n        \"every\": \"3h\",\n        \"target\": \"last\",\n        \"directPolicy\": \"allow\",\n        \"lightContext\": false,\n        \"activeHours\": {\n          \"start\": \"09:00\",\n          \"end\": \"18:00\",\n          \"timezone\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n        },\n        \"prompt\": \"Read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\"\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  \"tools\": {\n    \"elevated\": {\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"allowFrom\": {\n        \"feishu\": [\n          \"ou_0d8158fb9ce0f506ff8a89590d91c869\"\n        ],\n        \"openclaw-weixin\": [\n          \"*\"\n        ],\n        \"webchat\": [\n          \"*\"\n        ]\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  \"commands\": {\n    \"native\": \"auto\",\n    \"nativeSkills\": \"auto\",\n    \"bash\": true,\n    \"restart\": true,\n    \"ownerDisplay\": \"raw\"\n  },\n  \"channels\": {\n    \"feishu\": {\n      \"appId\": \"***\",\n      \"appSecret\": \"***\",\n      \"enabled\": true\n    }\n  },\n  \"gateway\": {\n    \"port\": 40062,\n    \"mode\": \"local\",\n    \"bind\": \"loopback\",\n    \"controlUi\": {\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"basePath\": \"/app/trim-openclaw/default\",\n      \"allowedOrigins\": [\n        \"*\"\n      ],\n      \"allowInsecureAuth\": true,\n      \"dangerouslyDisableDeviceAuth\": true\n    },\n    \"auth\": {\n      \"mode\": \"token\",\n      \"token\": \"***\"\n    },\n    \"trustedProxies\": [\n      \"127.0.0.1\",\n      \"::1\"\n    ]\n  },\n  \"plugins\": {\n    \"entries\": {\n      \"feishu\": {\n        \"enabled\": true\n      },\n      \"openclaw-weixin\": {\n        \"enabled\": true\n      },\n      \"memory-lancedb-pro\": {\n        \"enabled\": true,\n        \"config\": {\n          \"embedding\": {\n            \"provider\": \"openai-compatible\",\n            \"apiKey\": \"***\",\n            \"baseURL\": \"https://api.siliconflow.cn/v1\",\n            \"mode